  ],
  "remarks": "QDe.107. Reportedly defunct. Registered in Bosnia and Herzegovina as a citizens’ association under the name of “Citizens’ Association for Support and Prevention of lies – Furqan” on 26 Sep. 1997. Al Furqan ceased its work by decision of the Ministry of Justice of the Bosnia and Herzegovina Federation (decision number 03-054-286/97 dated 8 Nov. 2002). Al Furqan was no longer in existence as of Dec. 2008. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 15 Jun. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2253 (2015) was concluded on 21 Feb. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 15 November 2021. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.; Listing: Listed by the 1267 Committee on 11 May 2004 ( amended on 26 Nov. 2004, 24 Mar. 2009, 1 May 2019, 15 Nov. 2021, 30 Oct. 2023, 14 Dec. 2023 )",
